HEADWORD: Glowlamp
<hw>Glow"lamp`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>An aphlogistic lamp. See
<er>Aphlogistic</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Elect.)</fld> <def>An incandescent lamp. See
<er>Incandescent</er>, <pos>a.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glowworm</ent>⟦br⟧
